{"title":"oracle中 =: 和 :=","date":"2018-05-16T02:50:00.000Z","link":"post/74","tags":["procdure","变量","常量值","绑定","赋值"],"categories":["DataBase"],"updated":"2019-04-27T13:28:33.442Z","content":"<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">=: 后面是要接变量</span><br><span class=\"line\">:= 是在存储过程中中接常量值</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>例：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">=：应该相当于 a = :b 表明b是个绑定变量，需要执行时进行变量绑定</span><br><span class=\"line\">:= 相当于一般编程语言中的 赋值 a := 1 即将 数字1赋值给变量 a</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n","prev":{"title":"php的if和java的if比较","link":"post/108"},"next":{"title":"MYSQL中LIMIT用法","link":"post/73"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/74/"}